{
  "text": "Although the ratio of synovial\u00afuid to plasma concentrations approximates one, synovial membrane and bone concentrations are H10 times plasma concentrations [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Despite this, plasma kinetics appear unaltered, making it unlikely that intra-articular MTX will yield an advantage over systemic therapy [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
